{"tid":1747148,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"首投族：選票就是武器","createTime":"2019-11-23T05:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T10:54:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"10a37db7f7bb63b6538740f09d9b3d9971d607f7","tid":1747148,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:49:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191123/2ZFXLKOB2EUFW2UGTXR5PLQCHE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191123%2F2ZFXLKOB2EUFW2UGTXR5PLQCHE%2F&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpCBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=bd4605e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191123%2F2ZFXLKOB2EUFW2UGTXR5PLQCHE%2F&h=55c3df00\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191123/2ZFXLKOB2EUFW2UGTXR5PLQCHE/</a><br />\n<br />\n首投族：選票就是武器<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191123/large/1574438482_e40b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191123%2Flarge%2F1574438482_e40b.jpg&h=16aff6af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反送中運動令一班年輕人走上前線，亦令部份人明白區會有其影響性。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「覺得﹙區選﹚只係投班人出嚟咁囉！」19歲的港大生阿V，從前對區議員的印象，大約只是一班可有可無的街坊保長。直至反送中運動，各級議會如何扭曲民意有目共睹；人生首張選票，投於這個革命年代，阿V認為11.24投票日的「剔號」是表態、也是支持，不能在前線抗爭的人，明日的選票就是「武器」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「話畀政府聽我哋個取態」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：長者投票率一直遠超年輕人<br />\n<br />\n在前線度過不少日夜的阿V，自言從前也是和平理性，但6.9百萬人上街反送中，政府卻充耳不聞，林鄭政府改變了她：「係政府話畀我哋聽，和平係冇用，係要好多人出嚟，然後真係可能要去做一啲法律上唔容許嘅嘢，先至爭取到。」是這場運動，令她盡見建制把持的區議會，禁止討論所有反送中議案，「𠵱家覺得區議會有佢嘅影響性，如果投到唔係建制派、係真聽市民意見嘅議員，﹙政策﹚諮詢過程中，可阻攔唔想發生嘅事。」<br />\n<br />\n「冇能力走到咁前嘅人，區選就係一個好好嘅方法畀佢哋表態，話畀政府聽我哋個取態係點」，阿V作為大時代下的「首投族」，強調這次區選結果極具意義，若投票率低只會令人質疑港人是否有求變之心：「係咪我哋其實只係識得口講﹙爭取五大訴求﹚，但連投一張票咁簡單嘅行動都唔會做？」<br />\n<br />\n■記者許偉賢"},{"pid":"db3b9d41f0fd1aee300f9ad261928f67388bb7c9","tid":1747148,"uid":12517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:11:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>顯嘉請集中投5號</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/895184207211734/permalink/2692521227478014?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F895184207211734%2Fpermalink%2F2692521227478014%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpCBzIW6ugq8wWEqYO2LRYLo%3D&h=3a80e3d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/895184207211734/permalink/2692521227478014?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"6de2a54197d503ef9cd40aaa1d15173cb4e9e946","tid":1747148,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T06:49:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c93ec83d39cc9f701efc70f13ca7f3cf9654d47e","tid":1747148,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:48:12.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"2945560a87ce31874b5c3437ae1b62b35a6a0c10","tid":1747148,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T10:54:15.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}